cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.GR 

The paper deals with convolutional neural networks (CNNs) and their efficiency in exploiting spatial invariances. This is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG), as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses the estimation of vehicle and face poses, which falls under the category of graphics (cs.GR).
